<div class="container">
    <div class="container-box">
        <h2>What is BNSClans?</h2>
        <hr class="style12" />
        <p>BNSClans is a site made to help players organize their Blade & Soul clans and explore other clans. </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container-box">
        <h2>How does it work?</h2>
        <hr class="style12" />
        <p>
            After searching a clan name we go through a database to verify which players are in said clan. We 
            then update all data by comparing it to the live F2 page.
        </p>
    </div>
    <div class="container-box">

        <h2>Features</h2>
        <hr class="style12" />
            <ul>
                <li><p>Overview of clan, its members and their stats</p></li>
                <li><p>Compare clans and view rankings</p></li>
                <li><p>Overview of all registered clans</p></li>
                <li><p>Export and view clan avatars</p></li>
                <li><p>Sort tables to your own needs</p></li>
                <li><p>Filter shown stats and equipment</p></li>
                <li><p>Easily add members and update clans</p></li>
            </ul>
        <p><strong>Coming Soon</strong> (if the demand is there):</p>
