    <div class="container-box">
        <h2>What is this score?</h2>
        <hr class="style12" />

        <p>
            Score is calculated by taking into account all of your offensive stats and parsing it against 
            an average attack multiplier. You can see it as Coffee Score or DPS when holding LMB. 
            Item effects don't influence the calculation.
        </p>
